<br>
In fear the only changes noticed were to draco/cazic and the golems. They (the golems) hit for ~500, DT and drop random cazic stuff. Draco was downed on another server and supposedly dropped a CRoA and some new robe with +35 to all resists and 10ac. <p><BR>-Akahdrin Fatebringer, 58 Necroclerichantomancer
